OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1776041691
OL,3,CNorthern Premier League Chairman
OL,4,Csacked after telling fan 'go f***
OL,5,Cyourself'
OL,7,FA football league has relieved its
OL,8,Fchairman "of his duties" after he
OL,9,Femailed a fan "go f*** yourself".
OL,11,FFC United of Manchester fan Aled
OL,12,FDuckfield said the expletive-laden
OL,13,Femail came as a response to his
OL,14,Fmessage, expressing his concerns about
OL,15,Fthe teams' home fixture, in the
OL,16,FNorthern Premier League (NPL), being
OL,17,Fmoved to a neutral ground.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
