PN,39902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1776041691
OL,3,CNorthern Premier League Chairman
OL,4,Csacked after telling fan 'go f***
OL,5,Cyourself'
OL,7,FReplying to the email, Chairman Mark
OL,8,FHarris said: "Thank you for your
OL,9,Flovely email. Now go f*** yourself.
OL,10,FMark Harris."
OL,12,FAn NPL statement on Friday 10 April
OL,13,Fsaid: "Following a meeting of the
OL,14,Fboard, the Northern Premier League can
OL,15,Fconfirm that chairman Mark Harris has
OL,16,Fbeen relieved of his duties with
OL,17,Fimmediate effect, pending a full
OL,18,Fdisciplinary investigation."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
