PN,39903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1776041691
OL,3,CNorthern Premier League Chairman
OL,4,Csacked after telling fan 'go f***
OL,5,Cyourself'
OL,7,FFC United of Manchester released a
OL,8,Fstatement informing fans that their
OL,9,Fupcoming home fixture against Stockton
OL,10,FTown, based in Teeside, will be played
OL,11,Fat a neutral venue - Curzon Ashton
OL,12,FFC's The Tameside Stadium - at 7.45pm
OL,13,Fon 21 April.
OL,15,FIt said: "This decision has been made
OL,16,Funder the powers granted to the Board
OL,17,Fin accordance with Rule 8.7.2 of the
OL,18,FFA Standardised Rules.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
