PN,39904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1776041691
OL,3,CNorthern Premier League Chairman
OL,4,Csacked after telling fan 'go f***
OL,5,Cyourself'
OL,7,F"FC United of Manchester proposed an
OL,8,Falternative arrangement for the
OL,9,Ffixture, which was considered by the
OL,10,FBoard but not accepted."
OL,12,FFollowing the announcement, Mr Harris
OL,13,Fsaid: "The Board has determined that a
OL,14,Fneutral venue is the most appropriate
OL,15,Foutcome in this instance.
OL,17,F"The decision was made taking into
OL,18,Faccount the interests of both FC
OL,19,FUnited of Manchester and Stockton
OL,20,FTown."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1776041691
OL,3,CNorthern Premier League Chairman
OL,4,Csacked after telling fan 'go f***
OL,5,Cyourself'
OL,7,FFC United fan Aled Duckfield reached
OL,8,Fout to the Chairman via email, calling
OL,9,Fthe decision "diabolical".
OL,11,FHe said: "There is a chance we could
OL,12,Fwin the league at this fixture as well
OL,13,Fand to take this away from our
OL,14,Fsupporters from being in our own
OL,15,Fground shows the incompetence and lack
OL,16,Fof governance present at the NPL.
OL,18,F"You clearly have an issue with us,
OL,19,Fmaybe it's because we know how to do
OL,20,Fthings properly.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
