FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1776041691
OL,3,CNorthern Premier League Chairman
OL,4,Csacked after telling fan 'go f***
OL,5,Cyourself'
OL,7,F"At a time when non League clubs
OL,8,Fstruggle with cashflow, your decision
OL,9,Fwill cost our club and also lose our
OL,10,Fusual match day revenue.
OL,12,F"You are also making a laughing stock
OL,13,Fout of the integrity of this
OL,14,Fcompetition. You are now
OL,15,Fdisadvantaging the other competing
OL,16,Fteams for the playoffs by providing an
OL,17,Fadvantage to Stockton."
OL,19,FHe said the board should be "ashamed
OL,20,Fof themselves", urging the chairman to
OL,21,Fstand down from the board.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
